= Weapons =

'''Final Fantasy Mystic Quest''' features a streamlined weapon system where Benjamin (the hero) equips different weapon types, each with unique properties.

__TOC__

== Weapon Overview ==

Unlike traditional RPGs, FFMQ uses a fixed weapon progression system. Weapons cannot be bought or sold - they are found during the story.

